| в         | [](media/im |                          | /image185.wmf) |
| ычислений | age189.wmf) |                          |                |
+-----------+-------------+--------------------------+----------------+
| М         | !           | ![](media/image164.wmf)  | ![](media      |
| ежпроцес. | [](media/im |                          | /image191.wmf) |
|           | age190.wmf) |                          |                |
| связь     |             |                          |                |
